• TSWEB3: Inspired by the work of (Leacock et al., 1998), these Topic Signatures were constructed using monosemous relatives from WordNet (synonyms, hypernyms, direct and indirect hyponyms, and siblings), querying Google and retrieving up to one thousand snippets per query (that is, a word sense).
