Scale Knowledge Resources This study covers a wide range of large-scale knowledge resources: WordNet (WN) (Fellbaum, 1998), eXtended WordNet (Mihalcea and Moldovan, 2001), large collections of semantic preferences acquired from SemCor (Agirre and Martinez, 2001; Agirre and Martinez, 2002) or acquired from the BNC (McCarthy, 2001), largescale Topic Signatures for each synset acquired from the web (Agirre and de la Calle, 2004) or acquired from the BNC (Cuadros et al., 2005).
